  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed location of the awning above the fascia sign external to the shop front and the proposed design of the awning without a recessed mechanism would be harmful to the appearance of the building, would be out of character with the surrounding premises on Upper Street and would be detrimental to the character of the Angel Conservation Area. The proposal conflicts with the guidance set out in the Shop front Design Guide, Conservation Area Design Guidelines and policies D1, D4, D13 and D22 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002."
